{"title":"齐次坐标、线性代数与圆锥曲线-1","uid":"69c46b9206ea0522a8e522d7af48dd00","slug":"齐次坐标、线性代数与圆锥曲线-1","date":"2021-04-30T13:09:12.000Z","updated":"2021-04-30T13:09:12.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/齐次坐标、线性代数与圆锥曲线-1.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h2 id=\"简介\"><a href=\"#简介\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"简介\"></a>简介</h2><p>本文与其说是一篇文章，不如说是对于<a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/103884912\">这篇文章</a>的简化与总结。</p>\n<p>最终目的是通过引入尽可能少的外部假定，使得我们可以从一个更高的视角看高中的圆锥曲线题。</p>\n<h2 id=\"基础要素\"><a href=\"#基础要素\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"基础要素\"></a>基础要素</h2><p>观察一个任意二次曲线</p>\n<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><mi>A</mi><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mi>B</mi><mi>x</mi><mi>y</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>C</mi><msup><mi>y</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mi>D</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>E</mi><mi>y</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>F</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">Ax^2+Bxy+Cy^2+Dx+Ey+F=0</annotation></semantics></math></span>\n<p>首先，我们可以做如下换元：</p>\n<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><mo fence=\"true\">{</mo><mtable rowspacing=\"0.36em\" columnalign=\"left left\" columnspacing=\"1em\"><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mo mathvariant=\"normal\" lspace=\"0em\" rspace=\"0em\">′</mo></msup><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>x</mi><mi>z</mi></mfrac></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mrow><msup><mi>y</mi><mo mathvariant=\"normal\" lspace=\"0em\" rspace=\"0em\">′</mo></msup><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>y</mi><mi>z</mi></mfrac></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr></mtable></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\begin{cases}\n  x&#x27;=\\frac x z\\\\\n  y&#x27;=\\frac y z\\\\\n\\end{cases}</annotation></semantics></math></span>\n<p>其中<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>z</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">z</annotation></semantics></math></span>为任意实数，则我们可以有：</p>\n<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><mi>A</mi><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mi>B</mi><mi>x</mi><mi>y</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>C</mi><msup><mi>y</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mi>F</mi><msup><mi>z</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mi>D</mi><mi>x</mi><mi>z</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>E</mi><mi>y</mi><mi>z</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">Ax^2+Bxy+Cy^2+Fz^2+Dxz+Eyz=0</annotation></semantics></math></span>\n<p>我们均可以将其写成矩阵相乘的形式:</p>\n<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><msup><mrow><mo fence=\"true\">[</mo><mtable rowspacing=\"0.16em\" columnalign=\"center\" columnspacing=\"1em\"><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mi>x</mi></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mi>y</mi></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mi>z</mi></mstyle></mtd></mtr></mtable><mo fence=\"true\">]</mo></mrow><mi>T</mi></msup><mrow><mo fence=\"true\">[</mo><mtable rowspacing=\"0.16em\" columnalign=\"center center center\" columnspacing=\"1em\"><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mi>A</mi></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">/</mi><mn>2</mn></mrow></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mrow><mi>D</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">/</mi><mn>2</mn></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">/</mi><mn>2</mn></mrow></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mi>C</mi></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mrow><mi>E</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">/</mi><mn>2</mn></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mrow><mi>D</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">/</mi><mn>2</mn></mrow></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mrow><mi>E</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">/</mi><mn>2</mn></mrow></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mi>F</mi></mstyle></mtd></mtr></mtable><mo fence=\"true\">]</mo></mrow><mrow><mo fence=\"true\">[</mo><mtable rowspacing=\"0.16em\" columnalign=\"center\" columnspacing=\"1em\"><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mi>x</mi></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mi>y</mi></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mi>z</mi></mstyle></mtd></mtr></mtable><mo fence=\"true\">]</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\begin{bmatrix}\n  x \\\\ y \\\\ z\n\\end{bmatrix}^T\n\\begin{bmatrix}\n  A   &amp; B/2 &amp; D/2 \\\\\n  B/2 &amp; C   &amp; E/2 \\\\\n  D/2 &amp; E/2 &amp; F   \\\\\n\\end{bmatrix}\n\\begin{bmatrix}\n x \\\\ y \\\\  z\n\\end{bmatrix}\n= 0</annotation></semantics></math></span>\n<p>故我们可以用一个实对称矩阵来表示一个二次曲线。</p>\n<p>另外对于一条直线，如果我们做同样的换元，我们也可以以一个向量来表述它。<br>但为了不与点&#x2F;坐标产生歧义，我们约定后文以行向量表示直线，列向量表示点&#x2F;坐标。</p>\n<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>B</mi><mi>y</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>C</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>⟺</mo><mrow><mo fence=\"true\">[</mo><mtable rowspacing=\"0.16em\" columnalign=\"center center center\" columnspacing=\"1em\"><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mi>A</mi></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mi>B</mi></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mi>C</mi></mstyle></mtd></mtr></mtable><mo fence=\"true\">]</mo></mrow><mrow><mo fence=\"true\">[</mo><mtable rowspacing=\"0.16em\" columnalign=\"center\" columnspacing=\"1em\"><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mi>x</mi></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mi>y</mi></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mi>z</mi></mstyle></mtd></mtr></mtable><mo fence=\"true\">]</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">Ax+By+C=0 \\Longleftrightarrow\n\\begin{bmatrix}\n  A &amp; B &amp; C\n\\end{bmatrix}\n\\begin{bmatrix}\n  x \\\\ y \\\\ z\n\\end{bmatrix}\n= 0</annotation></semantics></math></span>\n<h3 id=\"小结\"><a href=\"#小结\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"小结\"></a>小结</h3><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>概念</th>\n<th>直角坐标系中</th>\n<th>矩阵表示的齐次坐标中</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>点</td>\n<td><span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><msub><mi>x</mi><mi>p</mi></msub><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><msub><mi>y</mi><mi>p</mi></msub><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">(x_p,y_p)</annotation></semantics></math></span></td>\n<td><span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">∀</mi><mi>z</mi><mo>:</mo><mrow><mo fence=\"true\">[</mo><mtable rowspacing=\"0.16em\" columnalign=\"center\" columnspacing=\"1em\"><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mrow><msub><mi>x</mi><mi>p</mi></msub><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">/</mi><mi>z</mi></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mrow><msub><mi>y</mi><mi>p</mi></msub><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">/</mi><mi>z</mi></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mi>z</mi></mstyle></mtd></mtr></mtable><mo fence=\"true\">]</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\forall z:\\begin{bmatrix} x_p/z\\\\y_p/z\\\\z \\end{bmatrix}</annotation></semantics></math></span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>直线</td>\n<td><span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>B</mi><mi>y</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>C</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">Ax+By+C=0</annotation></semantics></math></span></td>\n<td><span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mo fence=\"true\">[</mo><mtable rowspacing=\"0.16em\" columnalign=\"center center center\" columnspacing=\"1em\"><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mi>A</mi></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mi>B</mi></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mi>C</mi></mstyle></mtd></mtr></mtable><mo fence=\"true\">]</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\begin{bmatrix}A&amp;B&amp;C\\end{bmatrix}</annotation></semantics></math></span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>二次曲线</td>\n<td><span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>A</mi><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mi>B</mi><mi>x</mi><mi>y</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>C</mi><msup><mi>y</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mi>D</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>E</mi><mi>y</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>F</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">Ax^2+Bxy+Cy^2+Dx+Ey+F=0</annotation></semantics></math></span></td>\n<td><span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mo fence=\"true\">[</mo><mtable rowspacing=\"0.16em\" columnalign=\"center center center\" columnspacing=\"1em\"><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mi>A</mi></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">/</mi><mn>2</mn></mrow></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mrow><mi>D</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">/</mi><mn>2</mn></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">/</mi><mn>2</mn></mrow></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mi>C</mi></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mrow><mi>E</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">/</mi><mn>2</mn></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mrow><mi>D</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">/</mi><mn>2</mn></mrow></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mrow><mi>E</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">/</mi><mn>2</mn></mrow></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mi>F</mi></mstyle></mtd></mtr></mtable><mo fence=\"true\">]</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\begin{bmatrix}A&amp;B/2&amp;D/2\\\\B/2&amp;C&amp;E/2\\\\D/2&amp;E/2&amp;F\\\\\\end{bmatrix}</annotation></semantics></math></span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>点<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>p</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">p</annotation></semantics></math></span>在直线<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>l</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">l</annotation></semantics></math></span>上</td>\n<td><span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>l</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>p</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">l(p)=0</annotation></semantics></math></span></td>\n<td><span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>l</mi><mi>p</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">lp=0</annotation></semantics></math></span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>点<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>p</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">p</annotation></semantics></math></span>在二次曲线<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>c</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">c</annotation></semantics></math></span>上</td>\n<td><span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>c</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>p</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">c(p)=0</annotation></semantics></math></span></td>\n<td><span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msup><mi>p</mi><mi>T</mi></msup><mi>c</mi><mi>p</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">p^Tcp=0</annotation></semantics></math></span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h2 id=\"基础原语\"><a href=\"#基础原语\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"基础原语\"></a>基础原语</h2><h3 id=\"点线关系\"><a href=\"#点线关系\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"点线关系\"></a>点线关系</h3><p>我们都知道两相异的点可以定义出一条直线，两非平行直线也相交于一点。那么在其次坐标中会如何呢？</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>也可以选择把无穷远点看作两平行线交点，无穷远线看作相同两点连成的直线。<br>这样一样对偶。</p></blockquote>\n<p>首先看两直线的交点，若存在两直线<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>l</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><msub><mi>l</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">l_1,l_2</annotation></semantics></math></span>，则其交点<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>p</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">p</annotation></semantics></math></span>需要同时满足：</p>\n<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><mo fence=\"true\">{</mo><mtable rowspacing=\"0.36em\" columnalign=\"left left\" columnspacing=\"1em\"><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mrow><msub><mi>l</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mi>p</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mrow><msub><mi>l</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mi>p</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr></mtable></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\begin{cases}\n  l_1p=0\\\\\n  l_2p=0\\\\\n\\end{cases}</annotation></semantics></math></span>\n<p>可以看到这与立体几何中“求与两向量同时垂直的第三个向量”这一类问题拥有完全相同的形式。</p>\n<p>而这一问题最简单直接的解法就是作两向量的叉乘。但出于对偶性的要求，此处定义两行矩阵叉乘得到列矩阵，列矩阵叉乘得到行矩阵。</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>在向量意义上，简单地，叉乘可以定义为：</p>\n<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><mi>a</mi><mo>×</mo><mi>b</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>det</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow><mo fence=\"true\">(</mo><mtable rowspacing=\"0.16em\" columnalign=\"center center center\" columnspacing=\"1em\"><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mover accent=\"true\"><mi>i</mi><mo>⃗</mo></mover></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mover accent=\"true\"><mi>j</mi><mo>⃗</mo></mover></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mover accent=\"true\"><mi>k</mi><mo>⃗</mo></mover></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>3</mn></msub></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><msub><mi>b</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><msub><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><msub><mi>b</mi><mn>3</mn></msub></mstyle></mtd></mtr></mtable><mo fence=\"true\">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">a\\times b = \\det\\left(\\begin{matrix}\n\\vec i &amp; \\vec j &amp; \\vec k \\\\\na_1 &amp; a_2 &amp; a_3 \\\\\nb_1 &amp; b_2 &amp; b_3 \\\\\n\\end{matrix}\\right)</annotation></semantics></math></span>\n<p>其中,<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mover accent=\"true\"><mi>i</mi><mo>⃗</mo></mover><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mover accent=\"true\"><mi>j</mi><mo>⃗</mo></mover><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mover accent=\"true\"><mi>k</mi><mo>⃗</mo></mover></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\vec i,\\vec j,\\vec k</annotation></semantics></math></span>为各方向上的单位向量。<br>注意到：</p>\n<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mtable rowspacing=\"0.25em\" columnalign=\"right left\" columnspacing=\"0em\"><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"true\"><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>a</mi><mo>×</mo><mi>b</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>⋅</mo><mi>a</mi></mrow></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"true\"><mrow><mrow></mrow><mo>=</mo><mi>det</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow><mo fence=\"true\">(</mo><mtable rowspacing=\"0.16em\" columnalign=\"center center center\" columnspacing=\"1em\"><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mover accent=\"true\"><mi>i</mi><mo>⃗</mo></mover></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mover accent=\"true\"><mi>j</mi><mo>⃗</mo></mover></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mover accent=\"true\"><mi>k</mi><mo>⃗</mo></mover></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>3</mn></msub></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><msub><mi>b</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><msub><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><msub><mi>b</mi><mn>3</mn></msub></mstyle></mtd></mtr></mtable><mo fence=\"true\">)</mo></mrow><mo>⋅</mo><mi>a</mi></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"true\"><mrow></mrow></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"true\"><mrow><mrow></mrow><mo>=</mo><mi>det</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow><mo fence=\"true\">(</mo><mtable rowspacing=\"0.16em\" columnalign=\"center center center\" columnspacing=\"1em\"><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>3</mn></msub></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>3</mn></msub></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><msub><mi>b</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><msub><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><msub><mi>b</mi><mn>3</mn></msub></mstyle></mtd></mtr></mtable><mo fence=\"true\">)</mo></mrow></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"true\"><mrow></mrow></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"true\"><mrow><mrow></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr></mtable><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\begin{aligned}\n(a\\times b)\\cdot a &amp;= \\det\\left(\\begin{matrix}\n\\vec i &amp; \\vec j &amp; \\vec k \\\\\na_1 &amp; a_2 &amp; a_3 \\\\\nb_1 &amp; b_2 &amp; b_3 \\\\\n\\end{matrix}\\right) \\cdot a\\\\\n&amp;= \\det\\left(\\begin{matrix}\na_1 &amp; a_2 &amp; a_3 \\\\\na_1 &amp; a_2 &amp; a_3 \\\\\nb_1 &amp; b_2 &amp; b_3 \\\\\n\\end{matrix}\\right) \\\\\n&amp;= 0\n\\end{aligned}</annotation></semantics></math></span>\n<p>对于<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>b</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">b</annotation></semantics></math></span>同理，所以对于<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>c</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>a</mi><mo>×</mo><mi>b</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">c=a\\times b</annotation></semantics></math></span>，任取<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>λ</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><msub><mi>λ</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\lambda_1,\\lambda_2</annotation></semantics></math></span>，<br>我们有：<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>c</mi><mo>⋅</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><msub><mi>λ</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mi>a</mi><mo>+</mo><msub><mi>λ</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mi>b</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">c\\cdot (\\lambda_1 a+\\lambda_2 b) = 0</annotation></semantics></math></span></p></blockquote>\n<p>那么我们可以直接写出上述方程组的解：<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>p</mi><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>l</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>×</mo><msub><mi>l</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">p=l_1\\times l_2</annotation></semantics></math></span>。</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>严格意义上是解系<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>c</mi><msub><mi>l</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>×</mo><msub><mi>l</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">cl_1\\times l_2</annotation></semantics></math></span>，其中<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>c</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">c</annotation></semantics></math></span>是常数。</p>\n<p>但常数<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>c</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">c</annotation></semantics></math></span>大小与解在平面直角坐标系上的对应位置无关，故此处取<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>c</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">c=1</annotation></semantics></math></span></p></blockquote>\n<p>接下来看过两点的直线，若存在点<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>p</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><msub><mi>p</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">p_1,p_2</annotation></semantics></math></span>，则其连成的直线<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>l</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">l</annotation></semantics></math></span>满足：</p>\n<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><mo fence=\"true\">{</mo><mtable rowspacing=\"0.36em\" columnalign=\"left left\" columnspacing=\"1em\"><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mrow><mi>l</mi><msub><mi>p</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mrow><mi>l</mi><msub><mi>p</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr></mtable></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\begin{cases}\n  lp_1 = 0 \\\\\n  lp_2 = 0 \\\\\n\\end{cases}</annotation></semantics></math></span>\n<p>对等式两边翻转可以得到和上面一样的形式，故其解为：<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>l</mi><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>p</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>×</mo><msub><mi>p</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">l=p_1 \\times p_2</annotation></semantics></math></span></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>概念</th>\n<th>直角坐标中</th>\n<th>矩阵表示的齐次坐标中</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>直线<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>l</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><msub><mi>l</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">l_1,l_2</annotation></semantics></math></span>的交点</td>\n<td><span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>l</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>p</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>l</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>p</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">l_1(p)=l_2(p)=0</annotation></semantics></math></span> 的解</td>\n<td><span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>p</mi><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>l</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>×</mo><msub><mi>l</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">p=l_1\\times l_2</annotation></semantics></math></span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>过<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>p</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><msub><mi>p</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">p_1,p_2</annotation></semantics></math></span>的直线</td>\n<td><span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><msub><mi>x</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><msub><mi>y</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>−</mo><msub><mi>y</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>−</mo><msub><mi>y</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><msub><mi>x</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>−</mo><msub><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">(x-x_1)(y_1-y_2)=(y-y_1)(x_1-x_2)</annotation></semantics></math></span></td>\n<td><span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>l</mi><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>p</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>×</mo><msub><mi>p</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">l=p_1\\times p_2</annotation></semantics></math></span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h3 id=\"直线与点的线性组合\"><a href=\"#直线与点的线性组合\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"直线与点的线性组合\"></a>直线与点的线性组合</h3><p>注意到，对于两直线的交点<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>p</mi><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>l</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>×</mo><msub><mi>l</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">p=l_1\\times l_2</annotation></semantics></math></span>，对于任意<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>λ</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><msub><mi>λ</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\lambda_1,\\lambda_2</annotation></semantics></math></span>，<br>对两直线的线性组合<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>l</mi><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>λ</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi>l</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><msub><mi>λ</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi>l</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">l=\\lambda_1 l_1 + \\lambda_2 l_2</annotation></semantics></math></span>有：</p>\n<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mtable rowspacing=\"0.25em\" columnalign=\"right left\" columnspacing=\"0em\"><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"true\"><mrow><mi>l</mi><mi>p</mi></mrow></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"true\"><mrow><mrow></mrow><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>λ</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi>l</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mi>p</mi><mo>+</mo><msub><mi>λ</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi>l</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mi>p</mi></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"true\"><mrow></mrow></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"true\"><mrow><mrow></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr></mtable><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\begin{aligned}\nl p &amp;= \\lambda_1 l_1 p + \\lambda_2 l_2 p \\\\\n    &amp;= 0 + 0 = 0\n\\end{aligned}</annotation></semantics></math></span>\n<p>故可知其线性组合亦通过两直线的交点。这对应直角坐标系的一个直线系。</p>\n<p>对偶地，对于两点联结的直线:<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>l</mi><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>p</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>×</mo><msub><mi>p</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">l=p_1 \\times p_2</annotation></semantics></math></span>。对<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>p</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><msub><mi>p</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">p_1,p_2</annotation></semantics></math></span>的任意一个线性组合：<br><span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>p</mi><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>λ</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi>p</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><msub><mi>λ</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi>p</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">p=\\lambda_1 p_1 + \\lambda_2 p_2</annotation></semantics></math></span>。我们有：</p>\n<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mtable rowspacing=\"0.25em\" columnalign=\"right left\" columnspacing=\"0em\"><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"true\"><mrow><mi>l</mi><mi>p</mi></mrow></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"true\"><mrow><mrow></mrow><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>λ</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mi>l</mi><msub><mi>p</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><msub><mi>λ</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mi>l</mi><msub><mi>p</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"true\"><mrow></mrow></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"true\"><mrow><mrow></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr></mtable><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\begin{aligned}\n  lp &amp;= \\lambda_1 lp_1 + \\lambda_2 lp_2 \\\\\n     &amp;= 0 + 0 = 0\n\\end{aligned}</annotation></semantics></math></span>\n<p>其也在二者构成的直线上。</p>\n<p>这与直角坐标系上类似。</p>\n<h3 id=\"平行\"><a href=\"#平行\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"平行\"></a>平行</h3><p>注意一条特殊的“直线”<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>l</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">∞</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo fence=\"true\">[</mo><mtable rowspacing=\"0.16em\" columnalign=\"center center center\" columnspacing=\"1em\"><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mn>0</mn></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mn>0</mn></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mn>1</mn></mstyle></mtd></mtr></mtable><mo fence=\"true\">]</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">l_\\infty = \\begin{bmatrix} 0&amp;0&amp;1 \\end{bmatrix}</annotation></semantics></math></span>。</p>\n<p>其与任意直线<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>l</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">l</annotation></semantics></math></span>的线性组合<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msup><mi>l</mi><mo mathvariant=\"normal\" lspace=\"0em\" rspace=\"0em\">′</mo></msup><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>λ</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi>l</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">∞</mi></msub><mo>+</mo><msub><mi>λ</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mi>l</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">l&#x27; = \\lambda_1 l_\\infty + \\lambda_2 l</annotation></semantics></math></span>与<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>l</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">l</annotation></semantics></math></span>的交点均无法在直角坐标系内表示。</p>\n<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mtable rowspacing=\"0.25em\" columnalign=\"right left\" columnspacing=\"0em\"><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"true\"><mrow><msup><mi>l</mi><mo mathvariant=\"normal\" lspace=\"0em\" rspace=\"0em\">′</mo></msup><mo>×</mo><mi>l</mi></mrow></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"true\"><mrow><mrow></mrow><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>λ</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi>l</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">∞</mi></msub><mo>×</mo><mi>l</mi></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"true\"><mrow></mrow></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"true\"><mrow><mrow></mrow><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>λ</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mrow><mo fence=\"true\">[</mo><mtable rowspacing=\"0.16em\" columnalign=\"center center center\" columnspacing=\"1em\"><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mrow><mo>−</mo><msub><mi>l</mi><mi>y</mi></msub></mrow></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><msub><mi>l</mi><mi>x</mi></msub></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mn>0</mn></mstyle></mtd></mtr></mtable><mo fence=\"true\">]</mo></mrow></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr></mtable><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\begin{aligned}\nl&#x27; \\times l &amp;= \\lambda_1 l_\\infty \\times l \\\\\n &amp;= \\lambda_1 \\begin{bmatrix}-l_y &amp; l_x &amp; 0\\end{bmatrix}\n\\end{aligned}</annotation></semantics></math></span>\n<p>且其在平面直角坐标系上的表示正好与<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>l</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">l</annotation></semantics></math></span>平行。故我们可以将所有与<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>l</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">l</annotation></semantics></math></span>相差任意倍<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>l</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">∞</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">l_\\infty</annotation></semantics></math></span>的直线认为其与<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>l</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">l</annotation></semantics></math></span>平行。</p>\n<p>但对偶地，<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mo fence=\"true\">[</mo><mtable rowspacing=\"0.16em\" columnalign=\"center\" columnspacing=\"1em\"><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mn>0</mn></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mn>0</mn></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mn>1</mn></mstyle></mtd></mtr></mtable><mo fence=\"true\">]</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\begin{bmatrix} 0\\\\0\\\\1 \\end{bmatrix}</annotation></semantics></math></span>却代表原点。</p>\n","feature":true,"text":"简介本文与其说是一篇文章，不如说是对于这篇文章的简化与总结。 最终目的是通过引入尽可能少的外部假定，使得我们可以从一个更高的视角看高中的圆锥曲线题。 基础要素观察一个任意二次曲线 Ax2+Bxy+Cy2+Dx+Ey+F=0Ax^2+Bxy+Cy^2+Dx+Ey+F=0 首先，我们可以做如下换元： {x′=xzy′=yz\\begin{cases} x'=\\frac x z\\\\ y'=\\frac y z\\\\ \\end{cases} 其中zz...","permalink":"/post/齐次坐标、线性代数与圆锥曲线-1","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"3.8k","symbolsTime":"3 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"数学","slug":"数学","count":2,"path":"api/categories/数学.json"},{"name":"几何","slug":"数学/几何","count":1,"path":"api/categories/数学/几何.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"数学","slug":"数学","count":2,"path":"api/tags/数学.json"},{"name":"齐次坐标","slug":"齐次坐标","count":1,"path":"api/tags/齐次坐标.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%AE%80%E4%BB%8B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">简介</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E8%A6%81%E7%B4%A0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">基础要素</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%B0%8F%E7%BB%93\"><span class=\"toc-text\">小结</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-i